text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBvPIkxG", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 17, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8738692, "raw_content": "Mahabharata: The text describes Ashvatthama being possessed by the ferocious form of Shiva (known as Bhairava or Rudra) to massacre the Pandava camp.  It also details how Danavas and Rakshasas took possession of warriors like Bhishma, Drona, Kripa, and Karna (possessed by the soul of Naraka) to fight ruthlessly. Additionally, Nala is possessed by Kali (the personification of Kali Yuga), which perverts his mind.\nLinga Purana: This text narrates how Shiva possessed the body of a dead Brahmin using his yogic prowess (yogamayaya), resulting in the legendary figure Lakulisha. \nVedic Texts (Rig Veda): Verses reference the concept of gods possessing individuals or spaces, such as Soma and Rudra driving away illness that had possessed a dwelling, and munis (sages) being possessed by the wind or gods.\nMahabharata (Aryanyakaparva): The ascetic Vipula Bhargava is described as using yoga to enter and possess the mind and body of Ruci to protect her from Indra.", "author": "Tomis_4", "created": 1784576166144, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "God has never possessed humans. Jesus Christ taught us that demons possess humans and turn them wicked and evil. Hinduism is rooted in possessing humans. Hindu gods are demons! Any Christians who support Hinduism are committing blasphemy, an unforgiven sin!", "last_comment_created": 1784576166143, "content": "<p>Mahabharata: The text describes Ashvatthama being possessed by the ferocious form of Shiva (known as Bhairava or Rudra) to massacre the Pandava camp.  It also details how Danavas and Rakshasas took possession of warriors like Bhishma, Drona, Kripa, and Karna (possessed by the soul of Naraka) to fight ruthlessly. Additionally, Nala is possessed by Kali (the personification of Kali Yuga), which perverts his mind.\nLinga Purana: This text narrates how Shiva possessed the body of a dead Brahmin using his yogic prowess (yogamayaya), resulting in the legendary figure Lakulisha.\nVedic Texts (Rig Veda): Verses reference the concept of gods possessing individuals or spaces, such as Soma and Rudra driving away illness that had possessed a dwelling, and munis (sages) being possessed by the wind or gods.\nMahabharata (Aryanyakaparva): The ascetic Vipula Bhargava is described as using yoga to enter and possess the mind and body of Ruci to protect her from Indra.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 17, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBvPHeIJ", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 44, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8738227, "raw_content": "", "author": "TateDemarcus", "created": 1784557532288, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Feelsgood2020", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "cdn.5mind.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBvPHeIJ.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://cdn.5mind.com/uploads/production/mwOsjUdBTTVIBv-KCUusT/image/ncCD5hg6954CApsJlPUWG.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is